parameters:
Sorry, but this isn't that kind of shop, you
know... Well, it's fine, though...

This is a Lolimon dining specialty shop,
\C[1]Alvan-Tei\C[0]. I'm Alvan, the master here.
Do you have something you want to ask?

It seems like there was a demon attack in Rein
Garnet the other day, but it looks like we were
saved thanks to an amazing magical girl.

Sorry, but this isn't that kind of shop, you
know... Well, it's fine either way...

This is a Lolimon-exclusive dining establishment,
\C[1]Alvan-Tei\C[0]. I'm Alvan, the master of this
place.
Do you have something you want to ask?

It seems like there was a demon attack in Rein
Garnet the other day, but it looks like we were
saved thanks to an amazing magical girl.

From your sister Nefi, I have a package of
materials for you... and also the ones that were
missing... various things.

Oh, it's from Nefi. She usually shows up all the
time, so did something happen?

I heard there's an urgent quest. It seems a little
far, so I brought it here instead.

Oh, is that so? Well, it can't be helped. You
always come to the rescue...

Oh, that's right. Nefi, my step-sibling, was
helped by my parents in the past.

There are various reasons, but now we have become
a family. However, because she is a magical
girl... there are various worries.

Well, it's only natural for you to worry as an
older brother... It's nice, being siblings and
all.
There are no loli characters in your party.
What would you like me to do?
Please give me the cheapest one [500 Lo]
I guess I'll stop after all
一番安いやつでお願い【500Lo】

Hey! Don't wander around the kitchen dressed like
that!

I'm really good at cooking, but I hate doing it.
But it's my job, so I'm doing my best.

Did you get taken down by the enemy, perhaps? Take
care not to catch a cold.

I'm really grateful for this restaurant here. Even
someone like me, who's wild, can enter the store
without any problems, and the prices are
reasonable too.

Oh my, how indecent of you. How about you show
some respect for the place?

I want you to eat any delicious thing for the
loli-mon that protects you. I don't want to be
stingy about it, just this once.
What's that? Are you in heat or something?

We dragons are professionals when it comes to
battles, but well, in that area... we're a bit
weak when it comes to being on the receiving end.
No matter how much we trained, it didn't help... I
feel embarrassed saying that.

I'm sorry, I can't talk much right now. I need to
focus on eating...

I came all the way from the desert just to come
here, you know? The food here is delicious~! The
master is a nice person too, so I've completely
become a regular customer.
Huh? Are you a nudist? Don't you have any clothes?

It's a long time ago, but there was a village
where only fairies lived, dechiyo. Now it has
become a ruin, dechiyo... Bandits and such have
completely settled in, so be careful, dechiyo.
Ahahaha! I'm walking around naked! Ahahaha!

Eating the food here will greatly improve your
condition, especially when you eat your favorite
dish. The effects are tremendous.

Are you okay? I wonder if the enemies around here
were really that strong.
We have to raise Lolimon with love, you know.

Hey, cut me some slack~ Please put on some
clothes.

As long as the master we serve is reliable, us
loli monsters will be safe. There are some really
terrible ones out there, you know.

I can sense something very strong from you. You
must have a significant mission. Please take care.

Oh no, oh no! I don't have any clothes, but I have
bandages...!

Eating food here will make you feel very
energized! I ate a lot today too...

For the demons, we are just 'prey'. We are both
their prey to be devoured and their breeding
ground... We can't afford to lose, but...
Did it tear? Or is it just a hobby?

In the snowy region, there are many demons as
enemies, so it's important to properly train the
strong and formidable loli monsters. Of course,
your own strength is also crucial.

The other day, one of our comrades got captured by
a demon, and I tried to rescue them. But by the
time I saved them, they were already broken. If
that happens, us Lolimon are irreparable...

Because I'm such an idiot, I end up touching
anything that catches my interest. But whenever I
touch it, it usually unravels and disappears. I
wonder why that is?

Hey, don't you have a repair kit? Or do you enjoy
doing it?

Sometimes, the barrier pillars here get broken
too. I fix them before they are noticed by those
guys, so it's not a problem. But if there's a
quest, I have to accept it early and get it done.
Naked! No! My cock! It's getting bigger! No!

I'm not a lolimon. I'm a magical beast, but I've
got permission from my kind master. Don't worry, I
have some knowledge and I'm a bit strong, so I'll
protect the lolimons here.
Oh, my clothes... would you like to wear them...?

The magical beasts and goblins are completely
different. Those guys are scumbags, but it's tough
when you're surrounded by them... Be careful of
the goblins too.
What's this? Are we going for a swim?

If we have our comrades, we can dive into
suspicious water areas. However, we're not good
with places that are too deep. We're strong
against fast currents, though.
Hehe! I'm already here, you know!
Is that so! I relied on you as my comrade!
It's nice to have a good mood, isn't it?

If you learn the special field skills of the loli
monsters, you can receive various benefits. It
might be a good idea to listen to their requests
properly.
ここで単品アイテム入手
ここで単品アイテム入手
